{{Infobox dungeon |name = Spear Pillar |image = [[File:Spear Pillar.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Spear Pillar. |tokens = 84,500 |location = Mt. Coronet }} '''Spear Pillar''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Sinnoh]]. It initially has 64 tiles arranged in an 8x8 square, including 8 chest tiles, 19 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 1,322,100 HP.
